INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('29', '1', '2013-08-19 09:28:52', '2013-08-19 09:28:52', '<h1>An Aggressive San Antonio Criminal Attorney\r\nProviding Reliable Defense Services</h1>\r\n<h3>Proactive lawyer helping clients arrested or accused of DUI, DWI, drug possession, theft and sex crimes in San Antonio</h3>\r\nFounded in 1982, the Law Offices of Gary Churak, P.C.features the criminal defense services of Attorney Gary Churak, a dedicated and aggressive litigator with a reputation for success. Mr. Churak represents clients in cases ranging from juvenile offenses to violent crimes, providing consistent quality at affordable rates. His more than 30 years of legal experience make him a valuable resource for any questions you have throughout the legal process.\r\n<h3>Proactive, tenacious service aimed toward positive results</h3>\r\nWhen you face criminal charges, it’s important to contact an attorney as soon as possible. There are numerous factors that lead people to choose Mr. Churak as their criminal defense attorney, whether for San Antonio sex crimes, <span class=\"label label-important\">Important</span> drug defense or other matters:\r\n\r\nExperience. Mr. Churak has decades of experience as a San Antonio [label color=\"green\"]criminal defense[/label] attorney. Criminal law is what he does — he knows it inside and out and understands the tactics that provide the best chance of success in every scenario. He also knows when to work with the district attorney, and when to fight back.\r\n\r\nHands-on approach. As a sole practitioner, Mr. Churak handles every case himself. You rest easy knowing that you always have complete access to an attorney.\r\n\r\nMeticulous nature. Attorney Churak takes a full case history before doing anything so that he can analyze the details of your case. He also examines prior records to determine your best options moving forward.\r\n\r\nA convenient location. Most other firms are located downtown, but Mr. Churak’s San Antonio criminal defense law firm is much more convenient for local residents. He makes it easy to consult with an effective attorney when facing the criminal justice system.\r\n\r\nContact a criminal lawyer in San Antonio for more information\r\n\r\nCall the Law Offices of Gary Churak, P.C. today at [number type=\"1\"] or contact the firm online to schedule a free consultation. The firm’s phone lines are open 24 hours a day, seven days a week, with evening and weekend calls transferred directly to Mr. Churak. This allows you to stay up to date with the progress of your case at all times.', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'home', '', '', '2013-09-03 06:31:03', '2013-09-03 06:31:03', '', '0', 'http://preview.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/?page_id=29', '0', 'page', '', '0');
